OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"Dave Perry, lord of CaliforniaWh!( `|
OL,6,Bbased developer Shiny          Wz~}|3
OL,7,BEntertainment, has failed in   Wu ba
OL,8,Bhis aggressive bid to snatch   Woqs/a>
OL,9,Btwo hot young British games            
OL,10,Bdesigners from their comfortable beds. 
OL,12,F"If you read the recent Digitiser      
OL,13,Finterview with Mr Perry, you'll likely 
OL,14,Fhave a good idea who I'm talking about 
OL,15,F- but names still cannot be named.     
OL,16,FConfusion has arisen over whether the  
OL,17,Ftwo men will stay with their current   
OL,18,Femployer, or move on to an as-yet-     
OL,19,Funnamed firm. What larks!"             
