OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"In a not entirely unrelated   Wh!( `|
OL,6,Bpiece of news, work continues  Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bon the highly anticipated Tomb Wu ba
OL,8,BRaider 2. Core Design is       Woqs/a>
OL,9,Bleading development on the Saturn      
OL,10,B- the Derby firm's favourite format.   
OL,12,F"However, fitting all the special      
OL,13,Feffects into the game is proving a     
OL,14,Fdifficult task, and tests are underway 
OL,15,Fusing the cartridge add-on Sega has    
OL,16,Fdeveloped for Saturn Virtua Fighter 3. 
OL,18,B"But it's all very secret."            
