OL,1,R+%|l4|,$|,$s  n=j=|h<| k4|l4|l4W?4   
OL,2,Rr5z5s{5s{5  j5j5jws z%z5z5Wu#m'm
OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"The delays surrounding the    Wh!( `|
OL,6,Bdevelopment of Resident Evil 2 Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bcan be attributed to a sudden  Wu ba
OL,8,Bshift in focus.                Woqs/a>
OL,10,F"At a relatively late stage, the       
OL,11,Fdecision was made to make the game     
OL,12,Fless linear than the original classic, 
OL,13,Fand add alternative storylines to this 
OL,14,Fundead sequel.                         
OL,16,B"Increasing the characters' options in 
OL,17,Bthis way has doubled the size of the   
OL,18,Bgame - it'll now come on two CDs. Just 
OL,19,Blike my copy of Pink Floyd's The Wall!"
